# Info

Invoked when a level/dimension is loaded.

# Available Event Fields

- `event.level` - The level that was loaded

# Example

```js
LevelEvents.loaded(event => {
	console.log(`Level loaded: ${event.level.dimension}`)
})

// Listen for specific dimension
LevelEvents.loaded('minecraft:the_nether', event => {
	console.log('The Nether has been loaded!')
})
```
